frontmatter.title: Implementing base64 in rust
frontmatter.description: Honestly, i have a confession to make. I have used base64 numerous times, I know why you use it. I've had a vague understanding of how it is implemented. But i have never ever fully understood how it works. Until now. Lets implement a basic base64 program in Rust.
